<p>
  <span class="nym">Mauger</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>mahal</i> 'council, meeting' or <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> *<i>amal</i> 'vigor, bravery' + <span class="lang">Old High German</span>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>gēr</i> 'spear'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Cf. also <a class="nym" href="Amalger">Amalger</a>.</p>
</div>
  


